fields.name: creatine monohydrate powder - tropical, 1kg
fields.description: Our convenient creatine monohydrate powder is great for all your fitness goals. A popular ingredient in many all-in-one sports supplements, creatine increases your body’s ability to produce energy quickly. Creatine already exists in small amounts in our bodies naturally, but lots of people take it as a supplement to boost their performance in the gym. One of the most highly researched forms of creatine in the world — our hard-hitting creatine monohydrate powder is scientifically proven to increase physical performance, by improving overall power.
fields.ingredinets: Creapure Creatine Monohydrate (87%),  Flavouring (Acidity Regulator (Citric Acid),  Flavouring, Sweetener (Sucralose), Sunflower Oil, Colour (Beta Carotene).

fields.name: personal training 10 package
fields.description: The sessions are designed to include an entire workout, from warming up to unwinding. Of course, you can also choose to leave these parts out of the workout and instead focus the entire session on a longer program. It's a matter of taste, but since this has always been our most popular session, the length of the session seems to suit most people's needs. Of course, you spend more time with your PT every time you meet and this allows him / her to get a better idea of ​​your capabilities and needs. Our recommendation, if you have not tried our PT products before or if you are new to the training environment at the gym, is to start with our 55-minute sessions. You will get all the coaching you need to train properly for your goals and needs.

fields.name: pro smartshake 1L
fields.description: The Myprotein SmartShake Lite is the latest addition to our extensive range of sports supplement shakers. Standing at an impressive 1 litre capacity this shaker is ideal for those larger weight gain or meal replacement shakes, as well as doubling up as a water bottle keeping you hydrated during those intense training sessions. The concave hexagon shaped grill, unique to SmartShake, produces a smooth, lump-free shake, whilst the screw-on lid and 'flip-cap' ensure the SmartShake Lite is leak free. Made from high quality, durable BPA-free plastic, the SmartShake Lite is suitable for both dishwashers and microwaves.

fields.name: pro shakesphere black 700ml
fields.description: If you take nutrition seriously, this ShakeSphere Shaker is the choice for you. Made with a sleek matte black design, it features a leak-proof siding cap and silicone closure. Say goodbye to mixing balls or mesh grids, this shaker does all the work for you. Plus, its innovative rounded-edge design means that none of your powders will be left stuck in corners or edges — making it even easier to clean. With a massive 700ml capacity, it’s ideal for staying on top of your nutrition, wherever your day takes you.
